text: Amna Lihović (born 8 February 1997) is a Bosnian footballer who plays as a midfielder and has appeared for the Bosnia and Herzegovina women's national team. ==Career== Lihović has been capped for the Bosnia and Herzegovina national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. she plays for Qviding FIF. Previously she played for Jitex BK, Kungsbacka DFF.
